<SYNC Start=1337457><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1341925><P Class=ENCC>
집으로 가요
<SYNC Start=1343513><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1345359><P Class=ENCC>
