<SYNC Start=1449676><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1451038><P Class=ENCC>
말을 한다고
<SYNC Start=1453157><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1456766><P Class=ENCC>
집에 들어가서
<SYNC Start=1457991><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1458548><P Class=ENCC>
컴퓨터 디스크를<br>가져와야 돼
<SYNC Start=1461193><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1461483><P Class=ENCC>
