<SYNC Start=2878545><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2880794><P Class=ENCC>
아버지가 돌아가셨어
<SYNC Start=2882040><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2883301><P Class=ENCC>
